revisions.rev:
This is a '''list of soundtracks''' attributed to the [[drama CD]] and [[anime]] media types of the [[Japan]]ese series ''[[Angel Sanctuary]]''. Between 1999 and 2000 three CDs were released. The first was the soundtrack for the series of drama CDs, which cover the story of the Angel Sanctuary [[manga]]. The other two CDs were the soundtrack for the AS [[Original Video Animation|OVA]] and the opening single for the OVA.
==Angel Sanctuary Sound Track== {{Infobox Album | <!-- See Wikipedia:WikiProject Albums --> | Name = Angel Sanctuary Sound Track | Type = Soundtrack | Artist = Juri, Black Lily Sisters | Cover = | Released = April 21, 1999 | Recorded = | Genre = Drama CD soundtrack | Length = 66:41 | Label = | Producer = | Reviews = | Last album = | This album = | Next album = }} The '''Angel Sanctuary Sound Track''' was the first album released for the ''Angel Sanctuary'' series. It covers the BGM of the series of Drama CDs and was released on April 21, 1999.
